Standard. The relevant disclosure requirements covered in other environmental ESRS are:
(a) ESRS E1 Climate change, which addresses in particular GHG emissions and energy
resources (energy consumption);
(b) ESRS E2 Pollution, which addresses pollution to air, water and soil;
(c) ESRS E3 Water and marine resources which addresses in particular water resources
(water consumption) and marine resources;
1 EU Biodiversity Strategy for 2030- Bringing nature back into our lives, COM/2020/380 final.
